room_title: Escape room "The Lazarus Crystal" by Enigma HQ in San Diego
room_address: 1446 Front St. Suite 301 San Diego CA 92101
room_description: A former Enigma researcher, Gary Johnson, has left our organization for our archrivals, the Labyrinth, absconding with a magic crystal in the process. We’ll send you to Paris (no passport required) to decipher the crystal’s power and thwart our former colleague.
